s | Bind to workspace, trigger hydration |\r\n91. | `get_daemon_status` | lifecycle.rs | Report uptime, connections |\r\n92. | `get_workspace_status` | lifecycle.rs | Report code graph and content stats (modified) |\r\n93. | `index_workspace` | write.rs | Full AST parse + embedding |\r\n94. | `sync_workspace` | write.rs | Incremental index of modified files |\r\n95. | `map_code` | read.rs | List code nodes with filters |\r\n96. | `list_symbols` | read.rs | Search symbols by name/type/language |\r\n97. | `query_graph` | read.rs | Custom graph traversal (callers, callees, imports) |\r\n98. | `impact_analysis` | read.rs | Code-only impact of changes (modified) |\r\n99. | `unified_search` | read.rs | Vector + lexical search across code and content (modified) |\r\n100. | `get_health_report` | read.rs | Code graph health (modified) |\r\n101. | `flush_state` | write.rs | Serialize code graph to `.engram/` (modified) |\r\n102. | `index_git_history` | write.rs | Git commit ingestion (feature-gated) |\r\n103. | `query_changes` | read.rs | Git change tracing (feature-gated) |\r\n104. \r\n105. #### Models to Remove\r\n106. \r\n107. | File | Structs |\r\n108. |------|---------|\r\n109. | `src/models/task.rs` | `Task`, `TaskStatus`, `TaskRow` |\r\n110. | `src/models/graph.rs` | `DependencyType` (task dependency edges) |\r\n111. | `src/models/context.rs` | `Context`, `ContextRow` (task audit notes) |\r\n112. | `src/models/label.rs` | `Label`, `LabelRow` |\r\n113. | `src/models/comment.rs` | `Comment`, `CommentRow` |\r\n114. | `src/models/event.rs` | `Event`, `EventKind`, `EventRow` |\r\n115. | `src/models/spec.rs` | `Spec`, `SpecRow` |\r\n116. | `src/models/collection.rs` | `Collection`, `CollectionRow` |\r\n117. | `src/models/backlog.rs` | `BacklogFile`, `ProjectManifest` |\r\n118. \r\n119. #### Models to Retain\r\n120. \r\n121. | File | Structs |\r\n122. |------|---------|\r\n123. | `src/models/code_file.rs` | `CodeFile` |\r\n124. | `src/models/function.rs` | `Function` |\r\n125. | `src/models/class.rs` | `Class` |\r\n126. | `src/models/interface.rs` | `Interface` |\r\n127. | `src/models/code_edge.rs` | `CodeEdge`, `CodeEdgeType` |\r\n128. | `src/models/content.rs` | `ContentRecord` |\r\n129. | `src/models/commit.rs` | `CommitNode`, `ChangeRecord`, `ChangeType` |\r\n130. | `src/models/config.rs` | `WorkspaceConfig` (remove `CompactionConfig`, retain `CodeGraphConfig`, `EmbeddingConfig`) |\r\n131. | `src/models/registry.rs` | `RegistryConfig`, `ContentSource` |\r\n132. | `src/models/watcher.rs` | `WatcherEvent`, `WatchEventKind` |\r\n133. \r\n134. #### Database Tables to Remove\r\n135. \r\n136. | Table | Type | Purpose |\r\n137. |-------|------|---------|\r\n138. | `task` | SCHEMAFULL | Task records |\r\n139. | `label` | SCHEMAFULL | Task labels |\r\n140. | `comment` | SCHEMAFULL | Task comments |\r\n141. | `context` | SCHEMAFULL | Audit notes/decision records |\r\n142. | `spec` | SCHEMAFULL | Feature specifications |\r\n143. | `collection` | SCHEMAFULL | Named task groupings |\r\n144. | `event` | SCHEMAFULL | Immutable audit log |\r\n145. | `depends_on` | RELATION | Task dependency edges |\r\n146. | `implements` | RELATION | Task-to-spec edges |\r\n147. | `relates_to` | RELATION | General task relationships |\r\n148. | `concerns` | RELATION | Task-to-code linkage edges |\r\n149. | `contains` | RELATION | Collection membership edges |\r\n150. \r\n151. #### Database Tables to Retain\r\n152. \r\n153. | Table | Type | Purpose |\r\n154. |-------|------|---------|\r\n155. | `code_file` | SCHEMAFULL | Source file nodes |\r\n156. | `function` | SCHEMAFULL | Function/method nodes (with MTREE embedding index) |\r\n157. | `class` | SCHEMAFULL | Struct/type nodes (with MTREE embedding index) |\r\n158. | `interface` | SCHEMAFULL | Trait/protocol nodes (with MTREE embedding index) |\r\n159. | `calls` | RELATION | Function call edges |\r\n160. | `imports` | RELATION | File/module import edges |\r\n161. | `defines` | RELATION | File-defines-symbol edges |\r\n162. | `inherits_from` | RELATION | Class inheritance edges |\r\n163. | `content_record` | SCHEMAFULL | Ingested workspace content (with MTREE embedding index) |\r\n164. | `commit_node` | SCHEMAFULL | Git commit nodes (feature-gated) |\r\n165. \r\n166. #### Services to Remove\r\n167. \r\n168. | File | Purpose |\r\n169. |------|---------|\r\n170. | `src/services/hydration.rs` | Task hydration from `.engram/tasks.md`, `graph.surql` |\r\n171. | `src/services/dehydration.rs` | Task dehydration to `.engram/tasks.md`, `graph.surql`, `comments.md`, `collections.md` |\r\n172. | `src/services/event_ledger.rs` | Append-only event log with pruning |\r\n173. | `src/services/compaction.rs` | Task text truncation for archival |\r\n174. | `src/services/connection.rs` | Task-related workspace binding, status change audit note creation |\r\n175. \r\n176. #### Services to Retain\r\n177. \r\n178. | File | Purpose |\r\n179. |------|---------|\r\n180. | `src/services/code_graph.rs` | AST parsing, indexing, edge creation, embedding |\r\n181. | `src/services/parsing.rs` | Tree-sitter AST parsing |\r\n182. | `src/services/embedding.rs` | fastembed wrapper |\r\n183. | `src/services/search.rs` | Vector/hybrid search (remove task search domains) |\r\n184. | `src/services/ingestion.rs` | Registry-driven content ingestion |\r\n185. | `src/services/registry.rs` | `.engram/registry.yaml` loading |\r\n186. | `src/services/git_graph.rs` | Git history indexing (feature-gated) |\r\n187. | `src/services/config.rs` | `.engram/config.toml` loading |\r\n188. | `src/services/output.rs` | Response filtering/projection |\r\n189. | `src/services/gate.rs` | Rate limiting |\r\n190. \r\n191. #### `.engram/` Files to Remove\r\n192. \r\n193. | File | Format |\r\n194. |------|--------|\r\n195. | `.engram/tasks.md` | Markdown with YAML frontmatter (task definitions) |\r\n196. | `.engram/graph.surql` | SurrealQL RELATE statements (task dependency edges) |\r\n197. | `.engram/comments.md` | Markdown (task comments